title: Assat station
text:
Assat is a <a href="railway%20station">railway station</a> in <a href="Assat">Assat</a>, <a href="Nouvelle-Aquitaine">Nouvelle-Aquitaine</a>, <a href="France">France</a>. The station is located on the <a href="Toulouse%E2%80%93Bayonne%20railway">Toulouse – Bayonne</a> railway line. The station is served by <a href="Transport%20express%20r%C3%A9gional">TER</a> (local) services operated by the <a href="SNCF">SNCF</a>.
